nodes.text: Rund Jesela was a male Bothan operative who was joined the Rebel Alliance and served aboard Tansarii Point Station around 1 ABY. He helped test a spacer who claimed to want to help.

Rund Jesela appeared as a non-player character in the video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online-role playing game developed by Sony and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011.
